<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Fit Flick</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/aboutus.css">
</head>

<body>

    <section class="about-container">

        <div class="about-header">
            <h1>About Fit Flick</h1>
            <p>Fit-Flick is a modern menswear brand focused on delivering stylish, comfortable, and everyday fashion for
                men. Our goal is simple: combine clean design, premium fabrics, and affordable pricing so every man can
                dress confidently.
                We believe clothing should not only look good but also fit perfectly and feel comfortable throughout the
                day.
            </p>

        </div>
 
        <div class="about-grid">

            <div class="about-card">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    At Fit-Flick, our mission is to provide high-quality men’s clothing that combines style, comfort, and affordability. We focus on creating apparel that fits well, looks modern, and can be worn confidently in everyday life. Our goal is to help every man build a wardrobe that is simple, stylish, and reliable without compromising on quality.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-card">
                <h2>What We Do</h2>
                <p>
                    Fit-Flick specializes in modern men’s fashion, offering clothing designed for comfort, style, and everyday wear. We curate and sell high-quality apparel that fits perfectly and keeps up with current fashion trends. Our focus is to provide men with reliable wardrobe essentials that look good and feel comfortable all day.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-card">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>
                  Our vision is to build Fit-Flick into a trusted men’s fashion brand, known for delivering stylish, comfortable, and affordable clothing. We aim to make modern fashion accessible to every man while continuously improving quality, design, and customer experience.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

</body>

</html>